On Monday, November 21, Dr. Jill Biden will be delivering remarks at a ceremony at the Pentagon to mark the signing of a Memorandum of Understanding between the National Guard Bureau and Give an Hour. This collaboration is aimed at supporting the emotional well-being of Guard members and their families as part of Dr. Biden's Joining Forces initiative. Additionally, Dr. Biden will be participating in an in-studio interview with SiriusXM to highlight the work of Joining Forces and Give an Hour in changing the culture of mental health through the Campaign to Change Direction. The interview will be aired on SiriusXM's Urban View channel 126 on Thursday, November 24 at 6:00 pm ET.